      "description": "when I enable yarn.log aggregation\u00a0 and define\u00a0\r\n\r\nyarn.log-aggregation.retain-seconds=3600\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\nbut after 3600s\u00a0/app-logs/hive/logs-ifile\u00a0 can't decrease and many many file exists for a long time than 3600s before now;\r\n\r\nso how can I do so that the yarn.log can auto clean itself",
