              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Chicago"
            },
            "body": "I agree this looks very likely to be a duplicate of YARN-8279, although like that JIRA I'm confused as to why it is being reported against 2.7.5.  The index log aggregation format wasn't added until 2.9.",
